# Contributing to {{PROJECT_NAME}}

Thanks for your interest in contributing! This project was generated by
[ForgeCLI](https://github.com/cyberkallan/forgecli), so its structure is
uniform across every tool in the ecosystem.

## Development setup

```bash
git clone {{GITHUB}}
cd {{SLUG}}
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install pytest rich pyfiglet questionary
pip install -e .
```

## Project layout

```
{{SLUG}}/
├── main.py          entry point & menu loop
├── banner.py        ASCII banner rendering
├── ui.py            prompts + animated helpers
├── utils.py         system info, network checks
├── theme.py         runtime theme loading
├── installer.py     auto-installer for missing deps
├── updater.py       PyPI update checker
├── commands.py      all the command implementations
